        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="even-sect">
        <img src="images/takenot.png" alt="Cornell Style Notes">
        <div class="explanation">
            <h3>Cornell Notes</h3>
            <p>Take your notes in accordance to <b>"Cornell Note Taking Method"</b>. It is a very effective system to
                take organized notes and it renders your notes a lot more easy to review and study later.</p>
            <p>You should add keywords and a summary to your note to utilize this method however in Cornellus it is
                completely up to you to choose how you want to take your notes.</p>
            <p>Your notes are not shared with anyone, and is not visible by any other user.</p>    
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="odd-sect">
        <img src="images/calc.png" alt="Scientific Calculator">
