            <h3>Limitless Calculator</h3>
            <p>A scientific calculator to help you in your mathematics studies and daily calculations. The calculator
                can handle basic operations and scientific advanced operations.</p>
            <p>If you can think of anything that would be a good feature to add to the calculator, feel free to contact
                us.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="even-sect">
        <img src="images/pomo.png" alt="Pomodoro">
        <div class="explanation">
            <h3>Pomodoro App</h3>
            <p>Ever heard of <b>Pomodoro</b>? Pomodoro is a method of studying focused on increasing your effectiveness
                and discipline through long studies. Here is how it goes: </p>
            <p>You study for 25 minutes and then take a 5 minute break. After the fourth study session you should rest
                for 30 minutes. Cornellus gives you the option to start a fully automated session or control your breaks
                and study sessions.</p>
        </div>

